642    /**
643     * @throws Throwable
644     *
645     * @internal This method is not covered by the backward compatibility promise for PHPUnit
646     */
647    final public function runBare(): void
648    {
649        $emitter = Event\Facade::emitter();
650
651        $emitter->testPreparationStarted(
652            $this->valueObjectForEvents(),
653        );
654
655        $this->snapshotGlobalState();
656        $this->startOutputBuffering();
657        clearstatcache();
658
659        $hookMethods                       = (new HookMethods)->hookMethods(static::class);
660        $hasMetRequirements                = false;
661        $this->numberOfAssertionsPerformed = 0;
662        $currentWorkingDirectory           = getcwd();
663
664        try {
665            $this->checkRequirements();
666            $hasMetRequirements = true;
667
668            if ($this->inIsolation) {
669                // @codeCoverageIgnoreStart
670                $this->invokeBeforeClassHookMethods($hookMethods, $emitter);
671                // @codeCoverageIgnoreEnd
672            }
673
674            if (method_exists(static::class, $this->name) &&
675                MetadataRegistry::parser()->forClassAndMethod(static::class, $this->name)->isDoesNotPerformAssertions()->isNotEmpty()) {
676                $this->doesNotPerformAssertions = true;
677            }
678
679            $this->invokeBeforeTestHookMethods($hookMethods, $emitter);
680            $this->invokePreConditionHookMethods($hookMethods, $emitter);
681
682            $emitter->testPrepared(
683                $this->valueObjectForEvents(),
684            );
685
686            $this->wasPrepared = true;
687            $this->testResult  = $this->runTest();
688
689            $this->verifyMockObjects();
690            $this->invokePostConditionHookMethods($hookMethods, $emitter);
691
692            $this->status = TestStatus::success();
693        } catch (IncompleteTest $e) {
694            $this->status = TestStatus::incomplete($e->getMessage());
695
696            $emitter->testMarkedAsIncomplete(
697                $this->valueObjectForEvents(),
698                Event\Code\ThrowableBuilder::from($e),
699            );
700        } catch (SkippedTest $e) {
701            $this->status = TestStatus::skipped($e->getMessage());
702
703            $emitter->testSkipped(
704                $this->valueObjectForEvents(),
705                $e->getMessage(),
706            );
707        } catch (AssertionError|AssertionFailedError $e) {
708            if (!$this->wasPrepared) {
709                $this->wasPrepared = true;
710

1601    private function handleDependencies(): bool
1602    {
1603        if ([] === $this->dependencies || $this->inIsolation) {
1604            return true;
1605        }
1606
1607        $passedTests = PassedTests::instance();
1608
1609        foreach ($this->dependencies as $dependency) {
1610            if (!$dependency->isValid()) {
1611                $this->markErrorForInvalidDependency();
1612
1613                return false;
1614            }
1615
1616            if ($dependency->targetIsClass()) {
1617                $dependencyClassName = $dependency->getTargetClassName();
1618
1619                if (!class_exists($dependencyClassName)) {
1620                    $this->markErrorForInvalidDependency($dependency);
1621
1622                    return false;
1623                }
1624
1625                if (!$passedTests->hasTestClassPassed($dependencyClassName)) {
1626                    $this->markSkippedForMissingDependency($dependency);
1627
1628                    return false;
1629                }
1630
1631                continue;
1632            }
1633
1634            $dependencyTarget = $dependency->getTarget();
1635
1636            if (!$passedTests->hasTestMethodPassed($dependencyTarget)) {
1637                if (!$this->isCallableTestMethod($dependencyTarget)) {
1638                    $this->markErrorForInvalidDependency($dependency);
1639                } else {
1640                    $this->markSkippedForMissingDependency($dependency);
1641                }
1642
1643                return false;
1644            }
1645
1646            if ($passedTests->isGreaterThan($dependencyTarget, $this->size())) {
1647                Event\Facade::emitter()->testConsideredRisky(
1648                    $this->valueObjectForEvents(),
1649                    'This test depends on a test that is larger than itself',
1650                );
1651
1652                return false;
1653            }
1654
1655            $returnValue = $passedTests->returnValue($dependencyTarget);
1656
1657            if ($dependency->deepClone()) {
1658                $deepCopy = new DeepCopy;
1659                $deepCopy->skipUncloneable(false);
1660
1661                $this->dependencyInput[$dependencyTarget] = $deepCopy->copy($returnValue);
1662            } elseif ($dependency->shallowClone()) {
1663                $this->dependencyInput[$dependencyTarget] = clone $returnValue;
1664            } else {
1665                $this->dependencyInput[$dependencyTarget] = $returnValue;
1666            }
1667        }
1668
1669        $this->testValueObjectForEvents = null;
1670
1671        return true;
1672    }
